cs.WEB, cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.HC, cs.MM

The paper focuses on the performance evaluation of web ads, which falls under the category of web technologies. Therefore, cs.WEB is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses privacy and security concerns related to online advertising, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also analyzes the impact of web ads on webpage performance, which can be considered as a system performance evaluation (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the impact of web ads on user satisfaction and device energy consumption, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Finally, the paper analyzes the sources and delivery chain of web ads, which can be considered as a multimedia analysis (cs.MM).
